    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to people who make embroidery, which is needlework in which decorative designs are stiched into cloth, leather, or paper.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
